                                        README, Break down


Name space :SCOREAPP

Self-invoking anonymous function
    - Spinner

SCOREAPP.settings

SCOREAPP.controller
    - init

SCOREAPP.router
    - init
    - change
    - currentItem

SCOREAPP.touch
    - init (for swipe)


SCOREAPP.page
    - ranking
        - start spinner
        - make list item ranking current
        - get
        - parse
        - connect content tot data-route=ranking
        - stop spinner
        - send to change to active section

    - schedule
        - start spinner
        - make list item schedule current
        - get
        - parse
        - creat a link to go to game (so you can go to link with game id)
        - connect content tot data-route=schedule
        - stop spinner
        - send to change to active section

    - game
        - start spinner
        - make list item schedule current item
        - console.log shows game-id (pakID)
        - get
        - parse
        - connect content tot data-route=game
        - stop spinner


        - PostTeamData
            - console show when update the old and new scores
            - get value form select/option
            - make a string to send
            - make a XMLHttpRequest()
            - when send show a message in console log
        - when 'update' button click send
        - send to change to active section

Dom ready
    - start SCOREAPP.contoller.init

